quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,"'in aladhin ataqawa eiqab allah bifiel ma 'amarahum bih wtark ma nhahm enh, lahum eind rabihim fi alakhirat janaat fiha alnaeim almqym"
  68,35,"afnjel alkhadeyn lilah baltaet kalkafryn? ma lakum kayf hakamtum hdha alhukm aljayr, fsawytm baynahum fi althwab?"
  68,36,"afnjel alkhadeyn lilah baltaet kalkafryn? ma lakum kayf hakamtum hdha alhukm aljayr, fsawytm baynahum fi althwab?"
  68,37,"am lakum kitab manzil min alsama' tjdwn fih almtye kaleasy, fa'antum tadrusun fih ma tqwlwn? 'iina lakum fi hadha alkitab 'idhana ma tshthwn, lays lakum dhlk"
  68,38,"am lakum kitab manzil min alsama' tjdwn fih almtye kaleasy, fa'antum tadrusun fih ma tqwlwn? 'iina lakum fi hadha alkitab 'idhana ma tshthwn, lays lakum dhlk"
  68,39,am lakum ehwd wmwathyq ealayna fi 'anah sayahsul lakum maa turidun wtshthwn?
  68,40,"sal almushrikin -ayha alrswl-: 'ayuhum bdhlk alhukm kafil wdamn bi'an yakun lah dhlk? 'am lahum alihat tkful lahum maa yqwlwn, wteynhm ealaa 'iidrak ma tlbu, falyatuu biha 'iin kanuu sadiqin fi dewahm?"
  68,41,"sl almushrikin -ayha alrswl-: 'ayuhum bdhlk alhukm kafil wdamn bi'an yakun lah dhlk? 'am lahum alihat tkful lahum maa yqwlwn, wteynhm ealaa 'iidrak ma tlbu, falyatuu biha 'iin kanuu sadiqin fi dewahm?"
  68,42,"ywm alqiamat yshtd al'amr wyseb hwlh, wayati allah taealaa lifasl alqada' bayn alkhlayq, fayakshif ean saqih alkarimat alty la yshbhha shy', qal salaa allah ealayh wslm: \"ykshf rabana ean saqh, fysjd lah kl muwmin wmwmnt, wybqa man kan yasjud fi aldnya; rya' wsmet, fayadhhab lysjd, fyewd zahrih tbqana wahdana\" rwah albkhary wmslm"
  68,43,"mnksrt 'absaruhum la yrfewnha, tghshahm dhilat shadidat min eadhab allh, waqad kanuu fi aldunya yudeawn 'iilaa alsalat lilah webadth, wahum ashha' qadirun ealayha fala ysjdwn; tezzumana wastkbarana"
  68,44,"fdhrny -ayha alrswl- wman ykdhdhib bhdha alqran, fa'iina ely jza'hm walantqam mnhm, snmdhm balamwal wal'awlad walnem; astdrajana lahum min hayth la yasheurun 'anah sbb l'ihlakhm, w'umhlhm w'utyl aemarhm; liazdaduu 'ithmana. 'iina kaydi bahl alkufr qwy shdyd"
  68,45,"fdhrny -ayha alrswl- wman ykdhdhib bhdha alqran, fa'iina ely jza'hm walantqam mnhm, snmdhm balamwal wal'awlad walnem; astdrajana lahum min hayth la yasheurun 'anah sbb l'ihlakhm, w'umhlhm w'utyl aemarhm; liazdaduu 'ithmana. 'iina kaydi bahl alkufr qwy shdyd"
  68,46,"am tus'al -ayha alrswl- hwla' almushrikin 'ajrana dnywya ealaa tblygh alrisalat fahum min gharamat dhlk mkllafwn himla thqyla? bal aendhm eilm alghyb, fahum yaktubun eanh ma yahkumun bih lanfshm min 'anahum 'afdal mnzlt eind allah min 'ahl al'iiman bh?"
  68,47,"'am tus'al -ayha alrswl- hwla' almushrikin 'ajrana dnywya ealaa tblygh alrisalat fahum min gharamat dhlk mkllafwn himla thqyla? bal aendhm eilm alghyb, fahum yaktubun eanh ma yahkumun bih lanfshm min 'anahum 'afdal mnzlt eind allah min 'ahl al'iiman bh?"
  68,48,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- lamaa hakam bih rabik wqdah, wamin dhlk 'imhalhm wtakhyr nsrtk elyhm, wala takun kasahib alhwt, wahu yunis -elyh alslam- fi ghdbh wedm sabrah ealaa qwmh, hin nada rbh, wahu mmlw' ghmmana talbana tejyl aleadhab lhm, lawla 'an tadarakah niemat min rabih btwfyqh lltwbt wqabwlha laturih min batan alhut balard alfada' almhlkt, wahu at bima ylam elyh, fastfah rabih lrsalth, fajaealah min alsaalihin aladhin slht nyathm waemalhm waqwalhm"
  68,49,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- lamaa hakam bih rabik wqdah, wamin dhlk 'imhalhm wtakhyr nsrtk elyhm, wala takun kasahib alhwt, wahu yunis -elyh alslam- fi ghdbh wedm sabrah ealaa qwmh, hin nada rbh, wahu mmlw' ghmmana talbana tejyl aleadhab lhm, lawla 'an tadarakah niemat min rabih btwfyqh lltwbt wqabwlha laturih min batan alhut balard alfada' almhlkt, wahu at bima ylam elyh, fastfah rabih lrsalth, fajaealah min alsaalihin aladhin slht nyathm waemalhm waqwalhm"
  68,50,"fasbr -ayha alrswl- lamaa hakam bih rabik wqdah, wamin dhlk 'imhalhm wtakhyr nsrtk elyhm, wala takun kasahib alhwt, wahu yunis -elyh alslam- fi ghdbh wedm sabrah ealaa qwmh, hin nada rbh, wahu mmlw' ghmmana talbana tejyl aleadhab lhm, lawla 'an tadarakah niemat min rabih btwfyqh lltwbt wqabwlha laturih min batan alhut balard alfada' almhlkt, wahu at bima ylam elyh, fastfah rabih lrsalth, fajaealah min alsaalihin aladhin slht nyathm waemalhm waqwalhm"
  68,51,"wa'iin yakad alkufaar hin samieuu alquran lysybwnk -ayha alrswl- baleyn; lbghdhm 'iyak, lawla wqayt allah whmayth lk, wyqwlwn: -hsb ahwayhm- 'iinah lmjnwn"
  68,52,wma alquran 'iilaa maweizat wtdhkyr lilealamin min al'iins waljn